2. ❌ Forgetting to group guides into categories
3. ❌ Missing descriptions for guides
4. ❌ Inconsistent table formatting
5. ❌ Not explaining guides vs workflows difference
6. ❌ Missing navigation tips
7. ❌ Too verbose descriptions (keep to one sentence)
8. ❌ Not linking to related directories
9. ❌ Generic content that doesn't mention project name
10. ❌ Missing "Tip" at the end

